Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,======================================== TEXT ========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.64,0:00:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,香依
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我又没有朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.69,0:00:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.36,0:00:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 手机查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,谢罪的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,穿着正式 带上点心盒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,诚心诚意道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,正式的服装是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有体操服呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:00:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一里同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦 不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,被搭话了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.06,0:01:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不 现在不是这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.03,0:01:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次跟你说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你是一个班的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.76,0:01:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,本庄同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:30.65,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fn@方正粗圆_GBK\frz-90\c&H1A1F28&\fad(500,0)\pos(358.148,524.423)}本庄阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我叫本庄阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Comment: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,=======OP=======
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:18.67,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\c&HA66EF1&\pos(1782.412,803.769)}其实{\fs40\c&H9FA144&}是{\r\c&HA66EF1&}谢谢你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 让砂尾同学生气了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那真是头疼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,本庄同学人太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么那么警惕我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这是尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,老样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就来给你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,解决班上的问题也是副班长的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有体操服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要哭了 去和她好好讲清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎么让她生气的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就先说说一开始发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,海带和裙带菜的区别是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是口感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,分享烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有一样的烦恼的话 就一定能搞好关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就能跟菜子关系更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,等着我 菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cock-a-doodle-doo-ooo我觉得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:04:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还是不行 是我得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.89,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没法一上来问烦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我晚上就会觉得什么都能行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,波知 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上的我很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么突然说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,波知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一起在学校里探险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,入学还没去过的地方还有很多的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,和菜子学校探险…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,和菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,想去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,然后两个人休息的时候就在校舍里探险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为菜子是不喜欢到处走的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你好过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不过今天是特别的 可是探险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你手上拿的是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,说到探险 就是笛子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,随便走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,往上还是往下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你来决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那下面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,波知 要丢下你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,波知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是小卖部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,关着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,中午好像卖面包的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,下次来买买看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可疑的厕所呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可疑的厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真可疑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉有点什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有东西在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我很少被搭话的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得能交朋友就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,镜子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么有全身镜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,波知裙子那么长不好看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不好看的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候探险结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,已经要结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这次是在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就到了下午的课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,还有继续的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,上课时候想说话的时候传过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,信一样的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,向往很久的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,当做宝物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来去屋顶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,羊驼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,回信回信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,羊驼特征是全身软软的毛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但是是骆驼科的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,回的这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,然后两个人放学来到了屋顶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧 都变红了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,被和菜子搞好关系的书砸到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那什么书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还带着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 分享烦恼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那波知有什么想要告诉我的烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我的烦恼是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道怎么问菜子的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:09:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,已经解决了 现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没有解决
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,别哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那菜子的烦恼是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的烦恼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,入学以来就被奇怪的家伙跟着 这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,突然说想做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道想要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但很有行动力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不过嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,还挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我也能和那个人做朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说缠着菜子的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,能和我交朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,然后那天还好好的回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,然后今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,和全班都做朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么又
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,和小时候的伙伴 香依
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,和朋友约定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没有和全班交朋友就绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,全员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,香依是为了我好才这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始跟我搭话 也是因为和她的约定是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,引子好长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就不跟我说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么想原因都是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,本庄同学 为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你没察觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知何时说了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不用管那些的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 交给副班长我吧
Comment: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,===============
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,发的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,探险的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是很久以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上只过了几天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一里同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么换衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好好表达现在自己的心意她一定能理解你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,心意？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 想到的全部都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,全部全部全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,脚抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉既视感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始觉得菜子有些可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为和香依约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,才能够去搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为约定 才对菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,能喜欢上菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 要被误会的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是体操服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:11.89,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,休息的时候和菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:14.31,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,在校内探险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:16.21,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,问我上面还是下面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,看来没问题了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我就失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,误会还…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:23.06,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,然后突然发现可疑的厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这边还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:26.89,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,我吹笛子进了厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,波知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,波知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么生气的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是不懂的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,说了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你说想做朋友我很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:15:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你说谁都可以的话 我就很震惊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是谁都可以的 因为是菜子才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那是后面加的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始是其他动机的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始是因为你坐在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说震惊这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,全员都交朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 但是我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不是敬语了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要变回敬语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不过那个叫香依的 约定的也真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,约定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,波知 当了地主要让我住住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么约定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你有头绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,其他有谁能做朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,放弃思考了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:16:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 今天跟我搭话的那个人的话应该
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,应该不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,波知 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,能正常打招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好去搭话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别吐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你居然能第一天和我搭话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那是菜子先跟我说话的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 呕吐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那你也能高兴的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那被搭话了是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,本庄同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,和菜子和好的时候给我帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好体贴的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那个笑容很虚假的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,听见在谈论我了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,和砂尾同学和好了真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:16:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,体育系的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么还有衣架
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你衣架在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是早上比较赶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 我不会迟到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,平时时间都充足的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,潮流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就是潮流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我说怎么感觉是伪装的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是残念的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,残念？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说早上走得很急的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记穿内裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是妈妈的内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的呀 这是和妈妈一套的内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这也够残念了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 爷爷老家的习俗有这种的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,够残念了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,俗话说得好 母亲的内裤…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,残念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛 什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么暴露了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.23,0:18:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,本庄同学生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 做了多余的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 以为她不是好人就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,波知比较容易被骗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 看来不是坏家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 来笑我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我出生到现在一直都被说是残念的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以到了初中想要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,才参选了班长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可是结果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,副班长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,又是微妙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 为什么在铁棒上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才也在说我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,说我那么残念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是在说想和本庄同学交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,居然想和残念衣架的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,本庄同学才不残念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了本庄同学 我才能和菜子和好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那么体贴 那么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,脸算是可爱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你们干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住残念衣架的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我才没有开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她说不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,差一点了 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,能做朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为要和全班都做朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 就算没有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想和本庄同学交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她说不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 刚才是肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是能做朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照哦 一里同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,本庄同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,太高兴了就会昏迷的 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你能来扶一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前 有件事要跟砂尾同学说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.65,0:21:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的包
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.03,0:22:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不要用「你」称呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不要用「你」称呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.67,0:22:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要用「你」称呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,自尊心那么强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.78,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,明明那么残念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.69,0:22:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说我残念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很残念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,残念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
